videos.description: Isiah Thomas is in attendance to see Indiana take on North Carolina
videos.headline: Isiah Thomas is in attendance to see Indiana take on North Carolina

videos.description: James Blackmon Jr. drains a 3-pointer early in the first half to add to Indiana's fast start against No. 3 North Carolina.
videos.headline: Blackmon's 3-pointer adds to Indiana's hot start

videos.description: Former Indiana guard Isiah Thomas talks about the 1981 National Championship team and the basketball prestige of both Indana and North Carolina
videos.headline: Former Indiana guard Isiah Thomas talks about the 1981 National Championship team and the basketball prestige of both Indana and North Carolina

videos.description: 1H (11:13) IND James Blackmon Jr. made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Robert Johnson.
videos.headline: Indiana looks to put away North Carolina early with 3-point shot

videos.description: Indiana's Thomas Bryant cleans up a miss with a two-handed putback in the first half.
videos.headline: Bryant throws down powerful putback for Indiana

videos.description: OG Anunoby finishes a beautiful alley-oop pass from Josh Newkirk with one-handed dunk in the first half against North Carolina.
videos.headline: Anunoby throws down dazzling one-handed oop

videos.description: Indiana coach Tom Crean talks about his teams first half performance and how they have responded to the high intensity atmosphere
videos.headline: Indiana coach Tom Crean talks about his teams first half performance and how they have responded to the high intensity atmosphere

videos.description: Indiana honors Cubs outfielder and former Indiana baseball player Kyle Schwarber at the Indiana North Carolina game
videos.headline: Indiana honors Cubs outfielder and former Indiana baseball player Kyle Schwarber at the Indiana North Carolina game

videos.description: 2H (16:04) UNC Kennedy Meeks made Dunk. Assisted by Joel Berry II.
videos.headline: North Carolina looking to grab momentum off Kennedy Meeks dunk

videos.description: Thomas Bryant drains a deep 3-pointer as Indiana leads North Carolina in the second half.
videos.headline: Bryant drains deep 3-pointer for Hoosiers

videos.description: James Blackmon Jr. passes the ball off to OG Anunoby who drains three to extend No. 13 Indiana's lead over No. 3 North Carolina.
videos.headline: Anunoby knocks it in for three

videos.description: 2H (7:18) UNC Isaiah Hicks made Dunk. Assisted by Seventh Woods.
videos.headline: Isaiah Hicks throws down a powerful two-handed slam

videos.description: Justin Jackson picks up the Indiana miss and takes it to the other end, handing it off to Tony Bradley at the last second for a North Carolina dunk.
videos.headline: UNC's Bradley slams it home on fast break

videos.description:
2H (3:44) IND James Blackmon Jr. made Three Point Jumper.
2H (3:28) UNC Justin Jackson made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Joel Berry II.
videos.headline: Indiana and North Carolina trading 3-pointers in cloe game

videos.description: Indiana's OG Anunoby needs help off the court after appearing to injure his ankle coming down from a big dunk in the second half against North Carolina.
videos.headline: OG Anunoby lands awkwardly after dunk

videos.description: Indiana v North Carolina postgame breakdown on Indiana's fast start and great defense in their 76-67 upset win over No. 3 North Carolina
videos.headline: Indiana v North Carolina postgame breakdown on Indiana's fast start and great defense in their 76-67 upset win over No. 3 North Carolina

videos.description: OG Anunoby scores a team-high 16 points and James Blackmon Jr. adds 14 of his own to lead No. 13 Indiana past No. 3 North Carolina.
videos.headline: No. 13 Indiana upsets No. 3 North Carolina
